returns._owner: Address of the owner of the ETSTAG.

mint(string,address,address).details: Tag string must pass validation and publisher must be whitelisted.

params._creator: Address to be logged as creator.
params._publisher: Address to be logged as publisher.
params._tag: Tag string to mint - must include hashtag (#) at beginning of string.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

recycleTag(uint256).details: Token must exist, be not already be owned by platform and time of TX must be greater than lastTransferTime.

params._tokenId: The id of the ETSTAG being recycled.

renewTag(uint256).details: Can only be called by token owner.

params._ownershipTermLength: New length in unix epoch seconds.

params._accessControls: Address of the access controls contract.

upgradeTo(address).details: Upgrade the implementation of the proxy to `newImplementation`. Calls {_authorizeUpgrade}. Emits an {Upgraded} event.

upgradeToAndCall(address,bytes).details: Upgrade the implementation of the proxy to `newImplementation`, and subsequently execute the function call encoded in `data`. Calls {_authorizeUpgrade}. Emits an {Upgraded} event.

exists(uint256).notice: Existence check on a ETSTAG token.

getCreatorAddress(uint256).notice: Returns creator of a ETSTAG token.

getPaymentAddresses(uint256).notice: Returns the commission addresses related to a token.

ownershipTermLength().notice: Term length in seconds that a ETSTAG is owned before it needs to be renewed.

recycleTag(uint256).notice: Recycling an ETSTAG i.e. transferring ownership back to the platform due to stale ownership.

renewTag(uint256).notice: Renews an ETSTAG by setting its last transfer time to current time.

setOwnershipTermLength(uint256).notice: Admin method for updating the ownership term length for all ETSTAG tokens.

setPlatform(address).notice: Admin method for updating the address that receives the commission on behalf of the platform.

setTagMaxStringLength(uint256).notice: Admin method for updating the max string length of an ETSTAG.

tagToTokenId(string).notice: lookup of (lowercase) tag string to ETSTAG Id.

tokenIdToLastTransferTime(uint256).notice: Last time a ETSTAG was transfered.

tokenIdToTag(uint256).notice: Map of ETSTAG id to ETSTAG record.

tokenPointer().notice: Sequential integer counter for ETSTAG Id and total count.

updateAccessControls(address).notice: Admin functionality for updating the access controls.

userdoc.notice: Contract that governs the creation of ETSTAG non-fungible tokens.
